<commentary>īrṣyāmalaprakṣālanām āha.

parakīyaguṇavardhanavacaneṣu tatparitoṣaṇāya sādhu sādhu bhadrakam idam iti śabdam adhyāśayenoccārayet. kuśalakarmakāriṇam api dṛṣṭvā sādhu kṛtam dhanyo bhavān sukṛtakarmakārītyādibhiḥ stutivacanaiḥ protsāhayet.</commentary>

lapanāśaṅkāṃ nirasyann āha. paraguṇān sadbhūtān api parokṣaṃ brūyān na samakṣam.